---

import Italia_Drapeau from "~/assets/images/decor/italy.png";
import { Image }  from "astro:assets";
---


<div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center lg:items-start gap-8  mt-20">
    <!-- Première div avec flex en colonne -->
    <div class="flex flex-col w-full lg:w-2/5">
        <h1 class=" font-bold text-black text-6xl">Buongiorno</h1>
        <Image src={Italia_Drapeau} class="mt-10 pointer-events-auto" alt="Drapeau italien" width={128} height={128} />
        <p class="mt-10 text-gray-400 text-lg">
            Chez <span class="text-gray-600 font-semibold">La Carlina</span>, chaque interaction est une opportunité de tisser des liens, 
            de partager notre passion pour la gastronomie italienne et d’écouter ce qui rendra votre expérience inoubliable. 
            Que vous souhaitiez réserver une table sous les étoiles, ou simplement nous faire part de votre avis, nous sommes ici pour vous répondre.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-2">
            <!-- Adresse -->
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 rounded-lg transition cursor-pointer hover:text-brand-green">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 2C8.134 2 5 5.134 5 9c0 5.25 7 13 7 13s7-7.75 7-13c0-3.866-3.134-7-7-7z"></path>
                    <circle cx="12" cy="9" r="2.5"></circle>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-lg font-medium">8 Quai Albert Joly, 78250 Meulan-en-Yvelines</span>
            </div>
        
            <!-- Téléphone -->
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 rounded-lg transition cursor-pointer hover:text-brand-green">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-phone-call"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/><path d="M14.05 2a9 9 0 0 1 8 7.94"/><path d="M14.05 6A5 5 0 0 1 18 10"/></svg>
                <span class="text-lg font-medium">+39 06 1234 5678</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        
    </div>
    
    <!-- Deuxième div avec la map -->
    <div class="w-full lg:w-3/5">
        <iframe 
            src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d95045.95417114164!2d12.41816639313027!3d41.88885533356008!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x132f61dda264bafd%3A0xa710f5fca00d319c!2sVia%20di%20Ripetta%2C%2012%2C%2000186%20Roma%20RM%2C%20Italie!5e0!3m2!1sfr!2sfr!4v1740934012123!5m2!1sfr!2sfr" 
            width="100%" height="450" 
            style="border:0;" 
            allowfullscreen="" 
            loading="lazy" 
            referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade">
        </iframe>
    </div>
</div>
